source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements - White-Tailed Prairie Dog
source.description: This map shows the potential current distribution of white-tailed prairie dog, in the context of current and near-term terrestrial intactness and long-term potential for climate change and energy development.
